{"tid":797724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"TRUMP 據報收到北韓高層立場好戰信件後取消蓬佩奧訪朝","createTime":"2018-08-28T17:18:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-30T04:35:44.000Z","uid":79563,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2d9fe40888fb5c738235a13fcf970cfcd4c884a5","tid":797724,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:18:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1414972_1_L_20180828171447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1414972_1_L_20180828171447.jpg&h=41f16b6b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧上星期宣布將訪問北韓，但總統特朗普在數小時後決定取消。<br />\n<br />\n《華盛頓郵報》報道，特朗普是收到北韓高層官員一封立場好戰的信件而作出有關決定。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述兩名美國高級官員說，上星期五收到北韓勞動黨中央委員會副委員長金英哲的信件。報道未有提及信件內容，但信中好戰的立場，足以令特朗普取消蓬佩奧的訪問。<br />\n<br />\n金英哲之前數次代表北韓，同蓬佩奧會談。<br />\n<br />\n白宮拒絕回應，只叫傳媒向國務院查詢。"},{"pid":"12c0104fb089a97a8091782ba7cfede75a0d3a6a","tid":797724,"uid":4783,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"有傳係話北韓會不再會談，加上會恢復試射導彈同核試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a44d59ba5ae529141386142b30374131ee340ed","tid":797724,"uid":108347,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"12c0104fb089a97a8091782ba7cfede75a0d3a6a","tid":797724,"uid":4783,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:37:02.000Z","msg":"有傳係話北韓會不再會談，加上會恢復試射導彈同核試<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T17:44:36.000Z","msg":"真係信小熊<img src=\